node.name: $HAMMER Man
node.description:
$HAMMER is a memecoin on the HAM L3 Chain.

It is launched on mint.club, meaning it is attached to a bonding curve, which is basically a smart contract backed Liquidity Pool. You can always buy or sell $HAMMER. The more $HAMMER has been bought, the higher the price.

This tree is for regulating tipping allowances. An experiment for our Warpcast Channel and for the Mint.Club Bonding-Curve bound $HAMMER Token.

$HAMMER on Mint.Club: https://mint.club/token/ham/HAMMER
